Build a cinematic, fully animated single-page website for BREAKING BAD 
inspired by this Game of Thrones style — same structure, same scroll 
storytelling, same dark dramatic feel but with Breaking Bad theme.

=== DESIGN STYLE ===
- Dark background (#0a0a0a black)
- Neon blue/green meth crystal color accents (#00e5ff, #39ff14)
- Gold/amber text highlights like GoT but chemical-themed
- Cinematic serif font for headings (like Cinzel or Trajan)
- Particle effects: floating chemical molecule dots in background
- Every section is full viewport height (100vh)
- Smooth scroll with GSAP ScrollTrigger on every section

=== NAVBAR ===
- Top fixed navbar: "BREAKING BAD" logo left side
- Nav links right: THE WORLD | CHARACTERS | FACTIONS
- Gold underline separator below navbar (like GoT site)
- Semi-transparent dark background

=== SECTION 1 — HERO (like the ancient book opening) ===
- Full screen hero with a dramatic IMAGE of a chemistry flask/beaker 
  or a worn journal labeled "W.W." sitting on a desert table with 
  candles, matches, and chemistry notes around it
- Floating dust/ash particle animation in background
- Text fades in: "A CHEMISTRY TEACHER" (small gold label above)
- Main title: "THE BREAKING POINT" in huge serif font
- Subtitle italic: "In the beginning, there was only one rule — 
  don't get caught. He broke every one."
- Two CTA buttons: [BEGIN THE JOURNEY] [EXPLORE THE WORLD]
  (gold filled button + ghost outline button, like GoT)
- Scroll triggers a dramatic zoom-in on the journal

