- An abandoned RV appears in the distance through heat shimmer
- CSS heat shimmer/blur wave animation on horizon
- Text bottom left fades in:
  Small label: "WHERE IT ALL BEGAN"
  Big title: "THE DESERT COOK"
  Subtitle: "Miles from nowhere. The perfect place to disappear."
- Gold [BEGIN THE JOURNEY] button remains at bottom

