=== ANIMATIONS REQUIRED ===
- GSAP + ScrollTrigger for ALL scroll animations
- Parallax on every full-screen background image
- Particle system (floating molecules/dots) site-wide
- Card hover: 3D tilt effect + glow border
- Typewriter effect on quote wall
- Heat shimmer CSS animation on desert section
- Fade-in-up on all text blocks when entering viewport
- Smooth momentum scrolling throughout

=== TECH STACK ===
HTML + CSS + Vanilla JavaScript
GSAP CDN + ScrollTrigger plugin
No frameworks needed
Fully responsive (mobile + desktop)
All images use dark cinematic placeholder gradients if 
real images unavailable
